Recipe Vingrette.

Ingredients.
60 ml olijfolie
20 ml rode wijn azijn
5 g dijon mosterd
3 g zout
1 teentje knoflook

Method.
Put olijfolie into mixing bowl.
Add rode wijn azijn to mixing bowl.
Remove dijon mosterd from mixing bowl.
Combine teentje knoflook into mixing bowl.
Divide zout into mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.
